00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:44.260
You honor me with your presence.

00:04:44.260 --> 00:04:46.490
Thank you again.

00:04:46.490 --> 00:04:54.050
I'm humbled to talk in the
presence of some giants

00:04:54.050 --> 00:04:57.070
in this field of modern literature.

00:04:57.070 --> 00:05:01.730
I have my colleague Anna
