00:08:37.790 --> 00:08:43.020
Let's switch now to
Forough Farrokhzhad.

00:08:43.020 --> 00:08:46.100
I will tell you a little bit

00:08:46.100 --> 00:08:50.290
about my involvement
with Forough later on.

00:08:50.290 --> 00:08:55.080
But let me tell you
what I plan to do today.

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:58.760
As Fatemeh mentioned, I've been
working on Forough Farrokhzhad

00:08:58.760 --> 00:09:06.640
for 37 years and I am finally
finishing her biography.

00:09:06.640 --> 00:09:14.340
So it was really hard to condense
