00:09:15.410 --> 00:09:18.800
So I had to make certain decisions.

00:09:18.800 --> 00:09:24.950
So I'm going to focus first
and foremost on the biography

00:09:24.950 --> 00:09:29.370
of this iconoclastic icon.

00:09:29.370 --> 00:09:31.730
It's amazing that this woman

00:09:31.730 --> 00:09:40.180
who chose the penname Iconoclastic
[inaudible] has herself become a

00:09:40.180 --> 00:09:42.790
poet, an icon.

00:09:43.920 --> 00:09:52.370
But because there is so little
information about the first part

00:09:52.370 --> 00:09:59.260 position:56%
