00:35:16.110 --> 00:35:22.380
Now please consider the audacity
of a woman who is barely 20

00:35:22.380 --> 00:35:28.980
who goes unannounced, unknown
to the office of a magazine,

00:35:28.980 --> 00:35:31.990
finds her way to the
office of the editor

00:35:31.990 --> 00:35:35.070
in chief of the literary section.

00:35:35.070 --> 00:35:48.460 position:56%
And Mushisi looks at the poems and
