00:35:48.460 --> 00:35:55.510
It's a beautiful poem,
short poem, 12-line poem.

00:35:55.510 --> 00:36:00.200
[ Speaking foreign language ]

00:36:00.200 --> 00:36:01.780
"I sinned.

00:36:01.780 --> 00:36:05.560
I sinned voluptuously
in the arms of the man

00:36:05.560 --> 00:36:08.600
