00:36:08.600 --> 00:36:14.070
It's a reversal of thousands
of years of Persian literature.

00:36:14.070 --> 00:36:19.440
It was always men who
talked about their love

00:36:19.440 --> 00:36:22.210
for a woman or a feminized lover.

00:36:22.210 --> 00:36:28.690
And here was this woman
singing her love for a man.

00:36:28.690 --> 00:36:34.190
It was quite clear that it
was a woman writing for a man.

00:36:34.190 --> 00:36:38.950
And Mushidi was quite taken.

00:36:38.950 --> 00:36:49.570
She said she had two others
