the safety of the magazine,

00:36:59.330 --> 00:37:02.620
about the reaction of the people.

00:37:02.620 --> 00:37:06.590
And he consulted the
editorial board.

00:37:06.590 --> 00:37:10.560
And most of them wanted
the poem to be published.

00:37:10.560 --> 00:37:13.570
They thought it's a good
poem, it's interesting.

00:37:13.570 --> 00:37:16.930
It's a novelty.

00:37:16.930 --> 00:37:18.300
One person, Mr. [Foreign name],

00:37:18.300 --> 00:37:23.420
the editor in chief,
