00:41:11.930 --> 00:41:17.730
She takes full responsibility
for her act.

00:41:17.730 --> 00:41:23.180
Unlike most adulterous
women, and conveniently,

00:41:23.180 --> 00:41:26.290
she does not commit suicide.

00:41:26.290 --> 00:41:29.170
She does not kill herself.

00:41:29.170 --> 00:41:32.950
And she's not killed by some
mysterious disease either.

00:41:32.950 --> 00:41:41.550
She stays alive and she's
well and she's going to go on.

00:41:41.550 --> 00:41:44.730
So but I think even
more important than all

00:41:44.730 --> 00:41:50.440
of these things was the
layout of that first poem.

00:41:50.440 --> 00:41:51.860
Look at it.

00:41:51.860 --> 00:41:59.280
So this whole piece, most
of it is about her picture.

00:41:59.280 --> 00:42:03.640
I mean there are two pictures,
